data.description: WELCOME TO YOUR DREAM HOME IN ATLANTA!!!If you're a devoted fan of the Atlanta Falcons and Georgia Bulldogs and in search of the perfect residence with a dedicated man cave and an entertainment-ready vibe, your search ends here! This expansive 4500+ square foot home is situated on just over an acre, offering an ideal setting for your fan-filled family or gatherings. Boasting 5 bedrooms, 3 and a partially finished bath, this home provides ample space for all your needs. The additional loft space adds versatility, serving as a play area, office space, and more. The basement is thoughtfully designed with a workout area, theater space, and the ultimate game day entertainment hub--an absolute must-see in person. The master suite is truly a retreat, featuring a fireplace and a generously sized sitting area, providing comfort and convenience all in one room. Natural light floods the main level, accentuating the soaring ceilings. If you desire both space and the privacy of a cul-de-sac location, this is the home you won't want to miss. For a personal tour and to explore the unique features of this exceptional property, don't hesitate to reach out. Your dream home awaits!
